episodes.title: JW.org Cart crashing #4. Talking to a Jehovahs witness elder about false prophecies.
episodes.description:
This was a great open conversation with an active elder. Just stunning dialogue about how the NWT was mistranslated. A few topics covered. We left on friendly terms, and agreed to talk again. He seems like a genuinely nice human being. 

Sorry about the camera angle, i need to learn how to edit videos properly!

I look forward to the return visit 😎
